stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> PickIntent: inner retry loop
  PickIntent --> SamplePlan: bind intent domains keywords
  SamplePlan --> Simulate: ChainPlan ready

  state Simulate {
    [*] --> UserTurn
    UserTurn --> ToolLoop: history seeded
    state ToolLoop {
      [*] --> ResolveArgs
      ResolveArgs --> DedupeCheck
      DedupeCheck --> ExecuteMock: OK
      DedupeCheck --> DedupeCheck: skip duplicate
      ExecuteMock --> UpdateContext: tool message
      UpdateContext --> ResolveArgs: next step
    }
    ToolLoop --> FinalizeAssistant: all steps done or skipped
  }

  FinalizeAssistant --> BuildRecord: messages + metadata
  BuildRecord --> AnalyzeQuality: trace_analyzer
  AnalyzeQuality --> Validate: TraceValidator

  Validate --> Judge: pass or after repair
  Validate --> Repair: failures
  Repair --> Validate: re-check

  Judge --> Accept: mean score OK path
  Judge --> Repair: low score optional

  Accept --> CorpusUpdate: steering stats optional
  CorpusUpdate --> [*]: append JSONL row

  Validate --> Regenerate: hard fail e.g. zero tools
  Judge --> Regenerate: policy tags
  Regenerate --> PickIntent: retry budget
